# Tech Stack

Next.js 16 App Router + Prismic (Slice Machine) + CSS Modules + Vercel

## Conventions

- Server components by default. Only add `"use client"` when the component needs browser APIs, hooks, or event handlers.
- All CMS data fetching uses the Prismic client from `@/prismicio`.
- All content is modeled as slices in Slice Machine. Use Prismic MCP tools for modeling.
- Design tokens come from `@/lib/master-theme`. Never hardcode colors or font names.
- Company data comes from `@/lib/company`. Never hardcode addresses, phone numbers, or social links.
- All pages must have `generateMetadata()` pulling from Prismic SEO fields.
- i18n: all page routes are nested under `[lang]/`. Use `lang` param when fetching from Prismic.
